could possibly do this
job better than you can.

76
00:06:43,250 --> 00:06:46,083
And that's got nothing to
do with the aptitude tests.

77
00:06:46,166 --> 00:06:48,250
It's 'cuz I know what
you're capable of.

78
00:06:48,333 --> 00:06:51,125
"What needs to be done
is done by those capable.

79
00:06:51,208 --> 00:06:55,291
