Uh. I've been assigned to the
CID as of just yesterday ma'am.

85
00:08:14,208 --> 00:08:15,958
Inspector Akane Tsunemori.

86
00:08:16,041 --> 00:08:19,250
So you're the newbie
that shot down Shinya

87
00:08:19,333 --> 00:08:20,916
with the Paralyzer last night.

88
00:08:22,583 --> 00:08:24,833
Well you're a lot cuter
than I expected you to be.

89
00:08:24,916 --> 00:08:28,500
And ballsy. Look at you being
a little cutie with big balls.

90
00:08:28,583 --> 00:08:30,000
So what the hell happened?

91
00:08:30,083 --> 00:08:32,708
Let me guess, Shinya
tried to grab your ass, huh?

92
00:08:32,791 --> 00:08:34,750
No, that's not what--

93
00:08:34,833 --> 00:08:37,291
They told me that you're the one

94
00:08:37,375 --> 00:08:38,666
that you could tell me
how Kogami's doing?

95
00:08:38,750 --> 00:08:40,875
Ah. Of course.

96
00:08:41,708 --> 00:08:43,083
Can you believe the
government's got me

97
